quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,82,"Ŵanganyao akutiji: “Ana patuchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupaupape nambo yakuona uwwe tuchiukulidwa m’malembe?”"
  23,83,"“Chisimu tuŵele tuli nkupedwa chilanga uwwe ni achatatiŵetu chakwamba yalakweyi kuumila kalakala, nganiiŵa yalakweyi ikaŵeje adisiadisi syaŵandu ŵandanda.”"
  23,84,"Jilani: “Ana litaka ni yaili mwalakwemo yacheni nam’baga jenumanja ŵakumanyililaga?”"
  24,64,"Manyililani yanti! Chisimu yosope yaili kumawunde ni petaka ili ya Allah. Chisimu Jwalakwe jukumanyilila kaŵe kenu, ni (jukumanyilila soni) Lisiku lyatachiuchisyidwa ŵanganyao Kukwakwe, basi ni tachatagulila yaŵapanganyisye, soni Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwachimanya chenene."
  25,28,"“Ah kutapana kwangune! Nabolaga nga nganinantenda jwantijwanti kuŵa nsyoŵe.”"
  25,29,"“Chisimu pamasile paasochelesye une kwakuleka Chikumbusyo (Qur’an) panyuma pakumbichilila, soni shetani aŵele jwakunneka mundu (ngankamuchisya pa ipotesi).”"
  25,30,"Sano Ntenga ﷺ ni jwatite: “E Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵandu ŵangu ajitesile aji Qur’an kuŵa chindu chakulechedwa (pangajisooma ni ngakuuya malamusi gakwe).”"
  26,1,"Twâ-Sîn-Mîm. ",1:[Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.]
  26,2,"Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu chakusalichisya."
  26,3,"Mwinetu mmwe kuŵa nkulijonanga mwasyene (ni madandausi) ligongo lyanti ŵanganyao ngakuŵa ŵakulupilila."